subject: I can assure you my attitude
body: I can assure you my attitude to you has not changed, I`ll not betray you and will keep my word to help you. Let's go forward together and finish this project.

subject: Re:   I can assure you my attitude
body:
Hello! That sounds great. I appreciate your commitment to helping me with the project. Can you tell me more about how we can work together to get it done successfully?

Best wishes,
Maria

subject: Re:
body:
Oh My Darling,
You’re on my mind and in my heart. Keeping you close in my thoughts praying
for your health and courage to understand in order to listen to me in
trust, know that I’m thinking for you to give me a listening ear. It’s hard
to know what to say when you're going through hard times. It’s always a
good idea to stay out of any drama and just focus on doing what’s right and
being supportive and kindly do the things you have truly been doing by
having this accomplished.
Get more ideas about what to write not to come with mixed emotions. Your
message can focus on the positive aspects of the situation that will make
you feel good about the project as well as look forward to the future on
what an exciting privilege and with this wonderful opportunity all about
seeing that this happens takes a lot of determination when hard work, and
perseverance finally pay off. So happy for you to start your own business
investment plan and development project.
